HEADWORD: Elusory
<hw>E*lu"so*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>elusorius</ets>.]</ety> <def>Tending to elude or deceive; evasive;
fraudulent; fallacious; deceitful; deceptive.</def> --
